STRING <OR ATOM FALSE>)] 45>> 

"DCLOSE -- function to deactivate data base, flushing any
  current message" 

<SETG DCLOSE %<RSUBR-ENTRY '[SOPEN DCLOSE #DECL ("VALUE" <OR ATOM CHANNEL FALSE>
